727815f-c.title: Queens: Queens Boulevard - 65th Road
727815f-c.text:
Queens Boulevard, south side, epposite 65th Road, showing
three iews of the Geo. Englard house fermerly known as 830
Queens Boulevard. This house which was demolished in Karch 1925,
was erected hy the above individual on the site of an older house
that was demolished by fire.
April 1923
Views 1 and 2
View 3: February 1924.
Euugene L. Armbruater Collection
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
